 derived critical locus -- virtual cycles, perverse sheaves and\nmixed Hodge modules of vanishing cycles, and motivic Milnor fibres -- can be\ndefined for oriented d-critical loci and oriented d-critical stacks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Apr 2013 16:15:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 May 2013 08:28:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2013 10:01:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-08"}
